            <title><![CDATA[【🧋#三个月喝了近一千块的奶茶#】上海市消费者协会曾对奶茶进行过抽查，检测结果显示，27个奶茶店的51个奶茶品种中都含有大量咖啡因。[话筒]医生提醒，过量摄...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【🧋<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%88%E5%96%9D%E4%BA%86%E8%BF%91%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%83%E5%9D%97%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%88%E5%96%9D%E4%BA%86%E8%BF%91%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%83%E5%9D%97%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#三个月喝了近一千块的奶茶#</span></a>】上海市消费者协会曾对奶茶进行过抽查，检测结果显示，27个奶茶店的51个奶茶品种中都含有大量咖啡因。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>医生提醒，过量摄入咖啡因会影响身体健康。此外，奶茶含糖量较高，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%80%E6%9D%AF%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E5%90%AB%E7%B3%96%E9%87%8F%E7%BA%A6%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%80%E7%93%B6%E5%8F%AF%E4%B9%90%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%80%E6%9D%AF%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E5%90%AB%E7%B3%96%E9%87%8F%E7%BA%A6%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%80%E7%93%B6%E5%8F%AF%E4%B9%90%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#一杯奶茶含糖量约等于一瓶可乐#</span></a>，即使是在低糖、去糖或无糖奶茶中，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%97%A0%E7%B3%96%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%AB%E7%B3%96%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%97%A0%E7%B3%96%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%AB%E7%B3%96%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#无糖奶茶不是真的不含糖#</span></a> 👇🏻（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6YWmeB5" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
