            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[干饭人]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/cb/2022_Foodie_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%AD%E6%B5%B7%E9%A5%AE%E9%A3%9F%E6%88%96%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E8%82%A5%E8%83%96%E5%8F%91%E7%94%9F%E7%8E%87%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%AD%E6%B5%B7%E9%A5%AE%E9%A3%9F%E6%88%96%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E8%82%A5%E8%83%96%E5%8F%91%E7%94%9F%E7%8E%87%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#地中海饮食或降低肥胖发生率#</span></a>】地中海饮食以不饱和脂肪酸和优质蛋白质为主，能减少“痴呆症”患病风险，降低心脑血管疾病发生率和肥胖发生率，主要有以下特征：①建议食用全谷类食物，粗粮、杂粮等；②肉类来源以海产品、水产品为主，少吃红肉；③多吃新鲜蔬菜和水果；④建议烹调用橄榄油👇🏻 （央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6YNbKU4" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
